# API Service Project Structure

The API service is the core backend service. This guide documents the complete project structure and file organization for this service.

## Main Entry Points

- **Main Application**: [app.ts](mdc:src/app.ts) - Express.js application setup with middleware configuration and router mounting
- **Server Entry**: [server.ts](mdc:src/server.ts) - Server startup and initialization
- **Package Configuration**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies, scripts, and project metadata

## Directory Structure Overview

### Core Application
- **src/app.ts** - Main Express application configuration
- **src/server.ts** - Server startup and port binding
- **src/constants.ts** - Application-wide constants
- **src/index.d.ts** - TypeScript type declarations

### Routing Layer (`src/routers/`)
All API endpoints are organized by feature:
- **chat.ts** - Chat and conversation endpoints
- **webhooks/** - Webhook handlers for external integrations
- **users.ts** - User management endpoints
- **integrations.ts** - Third-party integration management
- **vendors.ts** - Vendor-specific endpoints
- **invite.ts** - User invitation system
- **organizations.ts** - Organization management
- **db-index.ts** - Database indexing endpoints
- **features.ts** - Feature flag management
- **jobs.ts** - Background job management
- **investigation.ts** - Investigation workflow endpoints
- **llm.ts** - Language model endpoints

### AI Agent System (`src/agent/`)
- **agent.ts** - Main AI agent implementation
- **callbacks.ts** - Agent callback handlers
- **helper.ts** - Agent utility functions
- **model.ts** - Model configuration and setup
- **parse.ts** - Input parsing utilities
- **prompts.ts** - System prompts and templates
- **vision.ts** - Vision model capabilities
- **rag/** - Retrieval Augmented Generation components
  - **chromadb.ts** - ChromaDB vector store integration
  - **pinecone.ts** - Pinecone vector store integration
  - **qdrant.ts** - Qdrant vector store integration
  - **index.ts** - RAG system entry point
  - **types.ts** - RAG type definitions
  - **utils.ts** - RAG utility functions
- **tools/** - Agent tool implementations
  - **base.ts** - Base tool interface
  - **constants.ts** - Tool-specific constants
  - **coralogix/** - Coralogix monitoring tools
  - **datadog/** - Datadog integration tools
  - **github/** - GitHub integration tools
  - **grafana/** - Grafana dashboard tools
  - **jaeger/** - Jaeger tracing tools
  - **mongodb/** - MongoDB database tools
  - **prometheus/** - Prometheus metrics tools
  - **static/** - Static utility tools
  - **experts/** - Expert system tools
  - **dummy.ts** - Testing/mock tools

