## Development Workflow

### Available Scripts
- `yarn dev` - Start development server with hot reload
- `yarn build` - Build TypeScript to JavaScript
- `yarn test` - Run test suite
- `yarn lint` - Run code linting
- `yarn typecheck` - Type checking without compilation
- `yarn deploy` - Deploy to production environment

### Environment Setup
- Development environment variables in `.env.dev`
- Production configuration through deployment scripts
- Tunnel support for webhook testing via ngrok